73
00:03:30,920 --> 00:03:32,610
if I was not so rigid,

74
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:35,330
would it be a different result?

75
00:03:36,010 --> 00:03:37,850
Just because I was too young

76
00:03:37,850 --> 00:03:39,050
to know how to adapt.

77
00:03:39,330 --> 00:03:41,050
