especially Lin Ge.

87
00:04:04,410 --> 00:04:05,730
Considering her family,

88
00:04:05,920 --> 00:04:07,480
she won't lose her mind.

89
00:04:09,410 --> 00:04:10,520
In my opinion,

90
00:04:11,890 --> 00:04:14,800
dating may not affect the training.

91
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:16,650
But breaking up will definitely affect it.

92
00:04:18,530 --> 00:04:19,650
So according to you,

93
00:04:19,650 --> 00:04:21,970
I should wish them a happy marriage, huh?

94
00:04:22,770 --> 00:04:24,440
Nothing has gone wrong with them.

95
00:04:24,440 --> 00:04:26,000
Can you stop getting involved?

96
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,730
Isn't this the same as saying nothing?

97
00:04:30,210 --> 00:04:31,050
By the way,

98
00:04:31,850 --> 00:04:33,090
you have to pay attention to Fang Chao.

99
00:04:33,530 --> 00:04:34,420
What's wrong with Fang Chao?

100
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:35,730
I think

101
00:04:36,090 --> 00:04:38,650
Fang Chao also has feelings for Lin Ge.

102
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:40,400
If...

103
