106
00:04:50,050 --> 00:04:51,000
Now that you mention it,

107
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:52,240
he does seem to be like that.

108
00:04:55,880 --> 00:04:58,440
Why are these kids so...

109
00:04:59,530 --> 00:05:01,800
How good and simple it was back then!

110
00:05:01,970 --> 00:05:04,000
We only knew about training. How vigorous!

111
00:05:04,650 --> 00:05:06,680
You're simple and stupid.

112
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:08,880
There were a lot of such things at that time.

113
00:05:09,170 --> 00:05:10,560
You were so stubborn

114
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:11,680
that no one was willing to tell you.

115
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:14,640
Really?

116
00:05:15,880 --> 00:05:17,410
Then tell me

117
00:05:17,920 --> 00:05:18,970
who you were with at that time.

118
00:05:20,970 --> 00:05:22,880
Excuse me. I'm ready to order.

119
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:37,410
I told you not to follow me.

120
00:05:39,210 --> 00:05:40,480
You've been avoiding me all day.

121
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:41,730
So what?

122
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:43,170
Then you get angry?

123
00:05:44,530 --> 00:05:45,560
How did I make you unhappy?

124
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:46,410
You can tell me.

125
00:05:46,730 --> 00:05:47,610
I can change.

126
00:05:48,320 --> 00:05:49,850
Or if you really don't like me,

127
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:50,970
you can also tell me.

128
00:05:51,410 --> 00:05:52,320
I can handle it.

129
00:05:53,320 --> 00:05:55,000
But don't let me guess what you are thinking.

130
00:05:55,170 --> 00:05:56,610
You know I can't do it.

131
00:05:57,410 --> 00:05:58,770
I've been thinking about it all day.

132
00:05:59,320 --> 00:06:01,210
Why on earth keeps you away from me?

133
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:03,090
Is it because you hate me

134
00:06:03,530 --> 00:06:05,240
or I make you unhappy?

135
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:07,290
Or is it because of girl's psychology

136
00:06:07,410 --> 00:06:08,770
mentioned online?

137
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:11,970
Did you check it online?

138
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:16,000
It's better not to check.

139
00:06:20,440 --> 00:06:22,680
I think my thinking is a little selfish.

140
00:06:23,560 --> 00:06:25,410
I haven't figured out how to tell you.

141
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:27,730
Even so, you still have to tell me.

142
00:06:28,090 --> 00:06:29,240
If it's too much,

143
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:30,480
