144
00:06:30,970 --> 00:06:31,810
How dare you!

145
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:32,770
Of course I dare.

146
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:34,970
What am I afraid of?

147
00:06:35,210 --> 00:06:36,880
Every time I encountered a problem,

148
00:06:37,290 --> 00:06:38,530
