164
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:26,880
I can't help but be angry and sad.

165
00:07:28,050 --> 00:07:29,770
I don't know what our relationship is.

166
00:07:30,050 --> 00:07:31,000
It's love.

167
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:10,610
Lin Ge, you have been avoiding me for a day.

168
00:08:10,780 --> 00:08:11,730
Because you learnt lessons

169
00:08:11,730 --> 00:08:13,730
