173
00:08:29,090 --> 00:08:30,170
I promise you.

174
00:08:58,600 --> 00:09:00,440
Fang Chao, what's the matter?

175
00:09:00,920 --> 00:09:01,760
Come in.

176
00:09:01,920 --> 00:09:03,320
(Room 306)
Wei went to other's room.

177
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:04,280
Come in and say it.

178
00:09:06,490 --> 00:09:07,330
Come on.

179
00:09:16,440 --> 00:09:17,290
Nothing's wrong.

180
00:09:18,410 --> 00:09:20,050
I noticed that your training condition

181
00:09:20,050 --> 00:09:20,890
is not very good today,

182
00:09:20,900 --> 00:09:21,760
so I came to check on you.

183
00:09:23,130 --> 00:09:24,440
Why are you starting to care

184
00:09:24,560 --> 00:09:26,320
about my training like Nie Chi?

185
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:32,040
Why

186
00:09:34,010 --> 00:09:35,890
