187
00:09:36,410 --> 00:09:37,680
What are you saying?

188
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:39,250
You've always cared about me.

189
00:09:40,170 --> 00:09:42,440
I noticed before we joined the team

190
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:46,530
that you can't stop talking about Nie Chi.

191
00:09:47,920 --> 00:09:48,760
I...

192
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:51,960
Why didn't I realize it?

193
00:09:54,080 --> 00:09:55,410
Then I'll be careful in the future.

194
00:09:59,900 --> 00:10:00,960
When you trained during the day,

195
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:02,560
the coach stared at you a few times.

196
00:10:03,050 --> 00:10:04,010
Take it seriously.

197
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:07,560
Don't worry, I'll adjust my condition.

198
00:10:09,050 --> 00:10:11,050
You're in the same dorm as Nie Chi.

199
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:12,440
You also help me remind him.

200
00:10:15,130 --> 00:10:17,560
No, I can't. You remind him.

201
00:10:17,650 --> 00:10:19,370
It's more appropriate.

202
00:10:19,920 --> 00:10:21,770
In fact, the two of us...

203
00:10:21,770 --> 00:10:22,610
That's it.

204
00:10:25,650 --> 00:10:26,680
That's it.

205
00:10:28,050 --> 00:10:29,010
I'm going.

206
00:10:34,680 --> 00:10:36,650
Is it that obvious?

207
00:10:48,410 --> 00:10:49,250
What's wrong?

208
00:10:50,490 --> 00:10:51,960
Look at Lin Ge.

209
00:10:52,440 --> 00:10:54,290
She's full of beans.

210
00:10:59,250 --> 00:11:00,090
A few days ago,

211
00:11:00,680 --> 00:11:03,440
she was depressed and you said it's bad.

212
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:05,290
Now she gets pumped up, it's not good either.

213
00:11:06,370 --> 00:11:07,410
It's so hard to satisfy you.

214
00:11:07,410 --> 00:11:09,490
It's not normal. Can't you tell?

215
00:11:10,560 --> 00:11:12,320
What can I do even so?

216
00:11:12,490 --> 00:11:13,370
I remind you

217
00:11:14,010 --> 00:11:16,290
these kids born after 1995 are different.

218
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:17,890
They are not like us back then

219
00:11:17,890 --> 00:11:19,320
when we listened to the coach.

220
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:21,840
They have their own ideas.

221
00:11:22,560 --> 00:11:23,840
If they really get emotional,

222
00:11:23,960 --> 00:11:24,840
let alone a coach,

223
00:11:25,250 --> 00:11:26,530
their parents are not working well.

224
00:11:28,130 --> 00:11:30,490
How about I give them a warning?

225
00:11:31,010 --> 00:11:31,850
No way.

226
00:11:32,960 --> 00:11:35,010
A friendly warning.

227
00:11:35,010 --> 00:11:35,850
Is it ok?

228
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:37,890
You handle it appropriately.

229
00:11:39,840 --> 00:11:41,920
You have a lot of things to do.

230
00:11:41,920 --> 00:11:43,080
What are you doing in my place?

231
00:11:43,080 --> 00:11:44,370
You affect the training, you know?

232
00:11:44,960 --> 00:11:45,840
I know.

233
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:48,440
The TV station needs someone to shoot.

234
00:11:48,920 --> 00:11:49,770
Why don't you go?

235
00:11:50,080 --> 00:11:50,920
No way.

236
00:11:51,250 --> 00:11:52,120
Can't we negotiate?

237
00:11:52,130 --> 00:11:52,970
We can't.

238
00:11:53,410 --> 00:11:55,490
Otherwise, I won't let them go.

239
00:11:56,920 --> 00:11:59,200
Fine. You go ahead.

240
00:12:14,490 --> 00:12:15,330
Let me tell you something.

241
00:12:16,370 --> 00:12:18,290
You know during this olympiad

242
00:12:18,720 --> 00:12:21,010
many players left the national team,

243
00:12:21,490 --> 00:12:22,440
some have retired,

244
00:12:22,890 --> 00:12:24,270
some have returned to the provincial team,

245
00:12:24,490 --> 00:12:26,170
and others went to study.

246
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:28,680
So the team discussed it and wanted

247
00:12:29,200 --> 00:12:31,650
to make an adjustment to your dorms.

248
00:12:32,800 --> 00:12:34,960
It won't be adjusted when the dorm is full.

249
00:12:35,490 --> 00:12:36,410
If it is not fully occupied,

250
00:12:36,410 --> 00:12:38,840
then put you together by events.

251
00:12:39,770 --> 00:12:40,610
Any problem?

252
00:12:40,920 --> 00:12:41,800
No.

253
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:45,920
Ok, I'll say a few more words.

254
00:12:47,200 --> 00:12:49,800
No matter which team you're in,

255
00:12:49,890 --> 00:12:52,200
you won't stay there forever.

256
00:12:52,530 --> 00:12:54,720
It's normal for people to come and go.

257
00:12:55,290 --> 00:12:56,170
In the national team,

258
00:12:56,170 --> 00:12:58,960
you can receive the highest level of training.

259
00:12:59,290 --> 00:13:00,170
Here,

260
00:13:00,490 --> 00:13:02,290
you live according to the olympiad.

261
00:13:02,770 --> 00:13:05,080
The time to compete in major tournaments

262
00:13:05,080 --> 00:13:06,170
is only a few years.

263
00:13:06,800 --> 00:13:08,650
Two olympiads for girls.

264
00:13:09,200 --> 00:13:11,080
A little longer for boys. Three olympiads.

265
00:13:12,010 --> 00:13:13,080
What I'm trying to say is

266
00:13:13,440 --> 00:13:14,890
I hope you can all

267
00:13:14,920 --> 00:13:17,290
cherish these years here

268
00:13:18,170 --> 00:13:19,560
and always remind yourself

269
00:13:19,680 --> 00:13:21,370
what you are doing here.

270
00:13:22,050 --> 00:13:23,800
Be worthy of the cultivation of the country.

271
00:13:25,010 --> 00:13:26,200
Be worthy of yourself.

272
00:13:29,440 --> 00:13:30,280
Understand?

273
00:13:30,920 --> 00:13:31,770
Understood.

274
00:13:32,560 --> 00:13:33,770
That's all for today.

275
00:13:36,680 --> 00:13:38,840
Lin Ge, what should we do?

276
00:13:38,840 --> 00:13:40,050
- Lin Ge.
- No worries.

277
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:42,160
Come here.

278
00:13:42,770 --> 00:13:44,080
You go back first. Don't worry.

279
00:13:45,600 --> 00:13:46,440
Mr. Li.

280
